#Hoare Logic for 

Hoare Logic Verification Tool: Dafny
Dafny Version: v4.11.0
---

The verification focuses on the 'normalizeGameStatus' function from the games and standings implementation.
The goal is to formally specify the correctness of the function for all supported game status inputs, aliases, normalized values and unknown cases.


##Running the Dafny verification tests:

### a)To install Dafny you could use the following command:
dotnet tool install --global dafny --version 4.11.0


### b) To run the verification test run the following command:
dafny verify "Tests/Hoare Logic/HoareLogicFullTest.dfy"



